defaultCase Study 2: 
defaultKier Minerals Ltd Greenburn Surface Coal Mine
defaultKier Minerals Ltd (part of Kier Group Plc)   currently own and operate a surface coal mine in the UK, the Greenburn Surface Mine, near New Cumnock in East Ayrshire. Reserves exist to continue until 2022.
defaultBy
default the end of August 2013 site ha
defaultd
default produced 5,492,00
default0 tonnes of coal 
